    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『モーター』が手に入りましたわ～！",
      "startTime": 3.1333333452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-suz001.wav",
      "text": "これで壊れてる所は、もうなさそうですわね！",
      "startTime": 5.9666666786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "後は燃料とかかな？　ここまで順調だね！",
      "startTime": 9.8559183875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-smr001.wav",
      "text": "この調子で、次の謎を探すぞ～！",
      "startTime": 14.4559183875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "よし、残るはあと『エネルギー』だけだ！",
      "startTime": 20.3625838715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh001.wav",
      "text": "次のヒントは……あれ？　このペン書けないぞ？",
      "startTime": 23.8727131953,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 49.87185879999956
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 49.87185879999956
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシ！",
      "startTime": 28.4304065504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr001.wav",
      "text": "またかかったゲシな、{user}！",
      "startTime": 30.190407733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "フフ……聞いて驚かないでおくれ。実は……",
      "startTime": 33.4637414096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-ktn001.wav",
      "text": "星見プロ中のボールペンのキャップを外しておいたんだ",
      "startTime": 40.2232652783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なっ……！　そんなの、インクがカピカピになって",
      "startTime": 44.1304101108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh002.wav",
      "text": "使えなくなるじゃないか！　どうしてそんなことを！",
      "startTime": 47.7225870887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自分が一番心当たりあるんとちゃいますか？",
      "startTime": 51.721112867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-smr002.wav",
      "text": "あんちゃん……さっきから怪しい行動してるやろ？",
      "startTime": 56.3477791904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実はさ～さっきこっそりそいつのポッケ縫い付けて",
      "startTime": 61.3877774992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-rio001.wav",
      "text": "開かないようにしてたら、偶然聞いちゃったんだけど～",
      "startTime": 65.0811125237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こいつ、さくら達と通信してたんだよ！？",
      "startTime": 69.4544441658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-rio002.wav",
      "text": "マシンがどうとか……マジありえなくない！？",
      "startTime": 73.6144458571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なっ！　勝手にポケットにイタズラしてたのか！？",
      "startTime": 77.2877815682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh003.wav",
      "text": "くっ……卑怯な！　小さいから気付けないじゃないか！",
      "startTime": 81.0892537553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "フフ……だが、マシンのことを知っているのは",
      "startTime": 85.867282466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-ktn002.wav",
      "text": "私達だけ……この中に裏切り者がいるってことになるね",
      "startTime": 91.0565986116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ユルセナイ……",
      "startTime": 97.2672829746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-suz002.wav",
      "text": "ウラギリモノ、ツブス……",
      "startTime": 99.4000000119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ガナ！　お前、ミボとブランに会いたくて",
      "startTime": 103.0006152907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr002.wav",
      "text": "泣いていたゲシな！？　怪しいゲシ！",
      "startTime": 106.6272805968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "ガナ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ひ、ひぃっ！　ミボちゃんとブランちゃんに",
      "startTime": 110.4672773797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "ガナ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-kan001.wav",
      "text": "会いたいのは本当だけど、私何もしてませんよぉ～！！",
      "startTime": 113.5606139301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うるさいゲシ！　ガナはてるてる坊主の刑にするゲシ！",
      "startTime": 119.5339476069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr003.wav",
      "text": "早くこっちに来るゲシ！",
      "startTime": 124.3939472634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バルゴ！　また怪しい動きが出来ないように",
      "startTime": 126.333943538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr004.wav",
      "text": "ポケットで見張っておくゲシ！",
      "startTime": 130.0606139301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（くそ……バルゴに見張られていて、うかつに動けない）",
      "startTime": 135.00061936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh004.wav",
      "text": "（時空の狭間はどんどん閉じていくし、どうすれば……）",
      "startTime": 139.4559199134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "見張りになれて好都合YOYO！",
      "startTime": 143.75154897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-hrk001.wav",
      "text": "次のヒントの場所を教えるエイヨー",
      "startTime": 146.4448768734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え！？　ヒントって……もしかして",
      "startTime": 149.618215128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh005.wav",
      "text": "バルゴさんが俺達を助けてくれてたんですか！？",
      "startTime": 153.2892532467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "やっぱりバルゴさんだったのか……！",
      "startTime": 156.4009360117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh006.wav",
      "text": "思ったより単純……いや、裏の裏をかいたんですよね！",
      "startTime": 158.9559199134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大声NG、お前に教示。ストレートには言えないけれど",
      "startTime": 163.7660624943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-hrk002.wav",
      "text": "次のヒントは『チラシ配り』　レッツゴー！",
      "startTime": 168.6927232224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バルゴさん、どうして俺達にそこまで……？",
      "startTime": 172.332729161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh007.wav",
      "text": "ザグラ達にバレたら、大変なことになるんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 176.5559199134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ザグラ達は元々善人！　昔はともに目指すトップ",
      "startTime": 179.7527311765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-hrk003.wav",
      "text": "アイドル！　厳しい芸能界に揉まれ変化！",
      "startTime": 183.6793827493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんだって！？　ザグラとバルゴさんも昔は",
      "startTime": 187.652721004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
